As a user who wants to play Battleship, I want a grid to put on my ships.
- Get a grid, user specify the size of the grid
- GUI
  - Grid
  - Ship images
- MouseEvents to select boxes on the screen
  - Click to draw X on the grid so the user knows they have put the ship
- Keyboard events to rotate the ship
-

As a user who wants to play Battleship, I want to input tiles to hit the opponent's ships

As a user who wants to play Battleship, I want a tally system so I know how many ships I've hit and when I have won

As a user who wants to play Battleship, I want to know what time it is because time is important

As a user who wants to play Battleship, I want to animation when I get a hit
